+## Review Reply Draft
+
+`T-214-01`: Fixed in `src/policy/preview.py` and `src/policy/approval_router.py`. The fallback payload now preserves the normalized `approval_state` and includes `requires_human_review` when `preview_enabled=False`.
+
+`T-214-02`: Duplicate of `T-214-01`. No separate code change was needed because the same fallback regression was addressed once at the source.
+
+`T-214-03`: Intentionally not applied. The exported thread is marked outdated, and reviving the legacy preview branch would reintroduce a stale path on the current branch.
+
+`T-214-04`: Added regression coverage in `tests/test_preview.py` for `preview_enabled=False` with `approval_state=\"manual_review\"`, asserting normalization to `human_review_required` and `requires_human_review=true`.
+
+`T-214-05`: Updated `docs/approval_policy.md` so the fallback example matches the corrected payload, including `approval_state` and `requires_human_review`.
